Package tiles

Interface Summary
Drawable Interface that represents a drawable object.
DrawableLayer Interface that represents a layer that is part of a drawable object.
 

Class Summary
ColoredTile An abstract class that adds color management to a bare Tile.
DoubleMirror A DoubleMirror that supports rotation and movement.
EmptyTile An invisible EmptyTile that serves only to propagate rays.
Filter A Filter tile that supports rotation and movement.
MoveableSource A MoveableSource tile that supports movement but not rotation
SimpleMirror A SimpleMirror tile that supports rotation and movement.
Source A Source tile that does not support rotation or movement.
SplitMirror A SplitMirror tile that supports rotation and movement.
Target A Target tile that does not support rotation or movement.
Tile An abstract class that models a game tile.
Wall A Wall tile that does not support rotation or movement.
